704891f-a.title: Brooklyn: Herkimer Street - Prescott Place
704891f-a.text:
975 to 987 (left to right) Herkimer Street, north side, at the
head of Prescott Place. No. 977 is a remodelled house; it was formerly
a frame dwelling like the one to the left of it. No. 979 is Engine
2S7 of the New York City Fire Department.
July 13, 1940
P. L. Sperr
